    {
      "id": "loop-runner",
      "title": "Deterministic loop runner",
      "description": "The plugin includes a deterministic runner that executes the safe automated parts of Research, Build, Verify, Test, and Reflect; records phase events; respects a slice budget; and marks the loop complete when evidence satisfies the vision.",
